  "description": "<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/30/aa8f852ffaa66e486101186dc6c8be40.jpg\" /></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<fieldset class=\"comment_quote\">\n\t\t<legend style=\"font-size: 16px; border-width: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></legend>\n\t\t<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n\t\t\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/10/17/62c1159770c52f599a301495788cd4f3.png\" style=\"height: 41px; width: 45px;\" /><span style=\"background-color: #0066cc;\"><span style=\"color: #e6e6fa;\"><strong>首先看一篇道歉信~</strong></span></span></p>\n\t\t<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n\t\t\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><b>要求：</b></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;\"><strong>You are the secretary of a computer hardware company. Write an email to Mr Gatt one of your customers, to apologise for the inconvenience created because he has not received an order. Mr Gatt&rsquo;s email address is joegatt@webcom.net.mt . You should write between 60 and 80 words</strong>.</span></p>\n\t\t<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n\t\t\t<span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;\">To: joegatt@webcom.net.mt</span></p>\n\t\t<p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n\t\t\tSubject: Missing Order</p>\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\tDear Mr Gatt,</div>\n\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<u>I am sorry to hear about the problems you have been experiencing</u> with the order you placed with us on the 23rd January.<strong>[1]</strong> I cannot as yet say who is at fault but I assure you there will be a full investigation.<strong>[2]</strong> Moyra Brown, who is our production assistant, will contact you shortly to arrange suitable compensation for the inconvenience that has been caused.<strong>[3]</strong></div>\n\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\tI would like to apologise once more.<strong>[4]</strong></div>\n\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\tYours sincerely,</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\tGeorge Hili</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</fieldset>\n\t<p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43);\">\n\t\t[0]这篇道歉信比较短，不知道日常生活中的道歉信是否也这么短。或许是因为对方本来就可能比较生气了，再发一篇长篇大论可能对方也不想看，对方其实就像知道问题怎么解决，后果谁承担。因此这篇邮件的逻辑基本也是按照这一顺序。</p>\n\t<p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43);\">\n\t\t[1]开头道歉。<span style=\"line-height: 28.7999992370605px;\">[2]然后可能会讲述问题原因，或者将解决方案先讲完，再解释原因（如果比较长）。</span></p>\n\t<p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43);\">\n\t\t<span style=\"line-height: 28.7999992370605px;\">[3]解决办法，越细越好，落实到人头和时间。这里用的shortly，或许发完邮件当天就会着手处理，但如果解决的时间比较长一些，或许应写明大约需要多少时间。</span></p>\n\t<p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43);\">\n\t\t[4]最后再次道歉。</p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; border: 0px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43);\">\n\t\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/10/17/62c1159770c52f599a301495788cd4f3.png\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; height: 41px; width: 45px;\" /><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em; background-color: rgb(0, 153, 204);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 250);\">再来看一篇非正式的邮件~</span></strong></span></p>\n\t<fieldset class=\"comment_quote\">\n\t\t<legend style=\"border-width: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></legend>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><b>要求：</b></span><strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">You cannot go for basketball practice. Write an email to your coach, George explaining why. George&rsquo;s address is george.xerri@vmail.com . You should use between 50 and 60 words.</span></strong></p>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\tTo: george.xerri@vmail.com</p>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\tSubject: Basketball Practice</p>\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\tHi George,</div>\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<u>I&rsquo;m really, really sorry </u>but I just can&rsquo;t make it for basketball practice this evening. We&rsquo;ve got a biology test tomorrow and I haven&rsquo;t yet started studying for it. I can&rsquo;t afford to fail the test, because I already failed the last one.</div>\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\tI promise to make up for it by the next practice session.</div>\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\tRon</div>\n\t</fieldset>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; border: 0px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43);\">\n\t\t*逻辑同上，首先道歉，然后解释原因，然后表明态度、补救措施&mdash;&mdash;<span style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">I promise to make up for it by the next practice session。由于比较简短，也并不非常正式，最后礼节性的结尾就省去了。</span></p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px; border: 0px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43);\">\n\t\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/10/17/62c1159770c52f599a301495788cd4f3.png\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; height: 41px; width: 45px;\" /><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em; background-color: rgb(0, 153, 204);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 250);\">来试一试~</span></strong></span></p>\n\t<fieldset class=\"comment_quote\">\n\t\t<legend style=\"border-width: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></legend>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t<strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">要求：</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">Write an email to Ms Sciberras, the school librarian, apologising for not returning the books on time. The school library email address is library88@gov.mt . You should write between 50 and 60 words.</span></strong></p>\n\t\t<p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n\t\t\t来试一试~</p>\n\t</fieldset>\n\t<fieldset style=\"border-width: 3px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 128, 0); font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 11px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); border-radius: 4px; line-height: 24px;\">\n\t\t<legend style=\"border-width: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Sample</legend>\n\t\t<p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n\t\t\t<strong>to:</strong><strong style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">library88@gov.mt</span></strong></p>\n\t\t<p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n\t\t\t<span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">subjectz: Library Books</span></p>\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\tDear Ms Sciberras,</div>\n\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<u>I would like to apologise for</u> not returning the books but I have been away from school for a week because I had the measles. I will not be coming to school for another week or so. I promise I will return the books as soon as I am back.</div>\n\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\tThank you.</div>\n\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\tRegards,</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\tAnita Borg</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</fieldset>\n\t<p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43);\">\n\t\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/27/ac2b0bf43f94380beeabf326f4b3f22c.png\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; height: 44px; width: 45px; float: left;\" /></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">对于相关内容有疑问或意见的请留言哦~</span></div><br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p867711/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p867711\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p914556/\">外媒：阿里巴巴双11再创记录 这牛X的购买力啊</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p914557/\">成语翻译：半信半疑&暴跳如雷</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p749165/\">英语四级作文：10个你想不到的总结句式</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p705156/\">BEC高级：巧用词汇句型，拿下图表作文</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p899297/\">双语美文：视野放宽，才能活得快乐自得</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p905050/\">史上最糟糕的学习方法，你中招了吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p850475/\">成功人士10种与众不同的思考路径</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p910871/\">Quora精选：如何最大化发挥你的学习能力？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p912747/\">感恩节真实来历 | 11月第4个星期四为何过节</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p779913/\">2016年12月英语六级听力场景600词（全）</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
